thread.title: TV | Homeland

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | Homeland
text: Well, what a shocker to leave things on last week in Homeland, as hitman Quinn receives his next target and it's none other than his former love Carrie Mathison. Surely he's not that dead inside to think about following through with it? We'll soon find out tonight. We reckon he will take one look at her and change his mind. Well - we hope. Also tonight, Carrie revisits her past with the help of Jonas.
